{"id":259566,"type":6,"name":"鹿鼎記","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2a/99/259566_Eewav.jpg","summary":"　　街市无赖韦小宝（汪禹 饰）阴差阳错进了宫，意外还和康熙皇帝（刘家辉 饰）打成一片，成了死党。随后，他更成了康熙的忠臣，帮康熙出谋划策，除掉了心腹大患鳌拜，一时官至极品，曾经的街市无赖终于出人头地。小宝也并非事事顺利，因其曾受天地会舵主陈近南所救，拜了陈近南为师傅，所以他在宫内的一大任务就是帮助天地会取得四十二章经。由于四十二章经关系重大，除了天地会、神龙教，甚至康熙都想查出其下落，小宝就在各方势力下鬼马周旋，最后更凭借其聪明才智成功脱身。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>鹿鼎记</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16038\">金庸</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/33303\">汪禹</a>、<a href=\"/person/17030\">劉家輝</a>、<a href=\"/person/33302\">谷峰</a>、<a href=\"/person/17337\">秦煌</a>、楚湘雲、尤翠玲</li><li><span>别名: </span>Tales of a Eunuch</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>语言: </span>粤语</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0200823</li><li><span>上映时间: </span>1983-03-24</li><li><span>片长: </span>90分钟</li><li><span>导演: </span>华山</li><li><span>编剧: </span>沈西城、司徒安</li>","eps":[{"id":825672,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/825672","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":16038,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3f/9d/16038_prsn_XvIGB.jpg","name":"查良镛","desc":"原作"},{"id":17030,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d1/57/17030_prsn_A7jUJ.jpg","name":"刘家辉","desc":"主演"},{"id":33302,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/44/6d/33302_prsn_0ww8F.jpg","name":"谷峰","desc":"主演"},{"id":33303,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d6/87/33303_prsn_svGQ6.jpg","name":"汪禹","desc":"主演"},{"id":17337,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1b/b8/17337_prsn_3o33O.jpg","name":"秦煌","desc":"主演"}],"relations":[{"id":123739,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/80/c2/123739_dCkY4.jpg","title":"鹿鼎記","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123739"},{"id":259564,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f6/a5/259564_xn5Mm.jpg","title":"鹿鼎記","type":"不同演绎","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/259564"},{"id":320077,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c6/e6/320077_f94k4.jpg","title":"鹿鼎记","type":"不同演绎","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/320077"}]}